Owlman 2023-04-05 4:53 AM
Ticketmaster has control over a huge part of the market (over 70%), to the point where nobody can compete with them. They also own Live Nation, who own and operate hundreds of venues, and even have a record label. It’s to the point where artists are basically forced to go them in one way or another. And Ticketmasters system is so messed up that it can’t handle huge tours, (think TSwift), and it’s broken enough that scalpers can easily abuse it. Add to that the fact that Ticketmaster doesn’t really have any incentive to fix it, cause people are forced to use them anyway. Here’s a fantastic video that explains the issues a little deeper: https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=FYE9Vepe68w&t=2s (edited)
Mic The Snare
The Real Reason Why Ticketmaster Sucks
